cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.NE, cs.CE 

The paper presents a framework that uses a neural network and an evolutionary algorithm for optimizing data-related parameters to estimate the remaining useful life of mechanical systems. This involves machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), neural networks (cs.NE), and computational engineering (cs.CE).
